sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Device
    participant Client as Zscaler Client Connector
    participant IdP as Identity Provider
    participant Z as Zscaler Cloud
    participant Policy as Policy Engine
    participant App as Application Server

    User->>Client: Launch private application
    Client->>Z: Forward access request
    Z->>IdP: Request user authentication
    IdP-->>User: Prompt credentials and MFA
    User-->>IdP: Submit verified identity
    IdP-->>Z: Send identity assertion and groups
    Z->>Policy: Evaluate identity, posture, location
    Policy-->>Z: Permit or deny decision
    alt Permit
        Z->>App: Broker secure outbound connection
        App-->>User: Provide application session
    else Deny
        Z-->>User: Block access and log event
    end